							<img src="https://www.suroboyo.web.id/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/monumen-resolusi-jihad-copy-p106j7tgoog4o9onbo67cr5mlovn4mqsl13nhn1c78.jpg" title="monumen resolusi jihad copy" alt="monumen resolusi jihad" />								</a>
